projects.expressionOutput: I love using watercolor paint as it is very fluid and freeing to use. The way water flows free and mixes colors together is beautiful. I love the paintings by Agnes Cecile as they are soft and show subtle emotion.
I love the use of acrylic paint, as you can get deep rich colors with this medium. Tanya Gomelskaya incorporates sculpture with acrylic paint to bring her paintings to life.
I am a fan of surreal photography, one of my favorite photographers is Sean Mundy. I like how you can take reality and morph it into something artistic.
I love dark illustrations, such as the work of Junji Ito. His heavy use of ink and lines, adds a dramatic effect to the dark stories he creates.
Cinema is an art form that I admire as well. One day I hope to create short films, like that of Ari Aster. I love the plot twists and cinematography choices used.
